name: Barrett Key Farm
improvements: The Barrett Key farm is a 222-acre Cotton and Soybean farm located 7 miles north of Kennett, Missouri in Dunklin County, Missouri. The "Bootheel" region of southeastern Missouri is known for its lighter soils and superb groundwater access.

name: Pine City Farm
improvements: Learn about our latest offering, the Pine City Farm, a 181 acre cotton and soybean farm in Dunklin County, Missouri. Located 2 miles south of Holcomb, MO. The farm consists of 3 tracts approximately 4 miles apart.
